            <title>[THRIFT-3712] TTornadoServer cannot handle IPv6 address</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3712</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TTornadoServer.handle_stream assumes its &quot;address&quot; argument to be a 2 tuple.&lt;br/&gt;
